  "text": "Thank you. When you spoke in the last session of energizing shocks coming from the top of the pyramid, did you mean that these came at intervals rather than steadily? I am raf these energizing shocks come at discrete intervals, but come very, very close together in a properly functioning pyramid shape in one whose dimensions have gone awry. The energy will not be released with regularity or in quanta as you may perhaps better understand our meaning.",
